\caption{
\textbf{Comprehensive Performance of SDAR vs. AR.}
Comparing strictly AR against SDAR across scientific and reasoning benchmarks.
\textsc{SDAR} achieves substantial gains in structured domains (e.g., Chemistry, GPQA) while maintaining parity or improving on general reasoning tasks.
\textbf{Bold} indicates the best result between the AR baseline and SDAR variants.
}

这一段 caption 缩短 3 个单词

这里删除了 "strictly" (副词修饰多余)、"baseline" 和 "variants" (上下文已明确，去掉了显得更干净)，正好缩短了 3 个单词以上，且语意保持完整。

```latex
\caption{
\textbf{Comprehensive Performance of SDAR vs. AR.}
Comparing AR against SDAR across scientific and reasoning benchmarks.
\textsc{SDAR} achieves substantial gains in structured domains (e.g., Chemistry, GPQA) while maintaining parity or improving on general reasoning tasks.
\textbf{Bold} indicates the best result between AR and SDAR.
}
```
